metadata.description: CBRD Mixed Breeds is the second generative NFT collection from Chef Boi R Doge, following the Mutts collection. Holders of a CBRD Mutt may claim a Mixed Breed for free (one per Mutt owned)! There are 10k Mutts and 15k Mixed Breeds. Visit ChefBoiRDoge.com for details and links. Commercial rights for each CBRD Mixed Breed NFT passes to the NFT holder!
metadata.name: Chef Boi R Doge: Mixed Breeds (CBRDM) #1
